column2: The Principal of Darkness ran towards RTC Medical Prep at 4m/s
The Principal of Darkness quickly sprinted towards the car.
The Principal of Darkness starts at RTC but rolls towards the car speeding up.
The Principal of Darkness accelerated towards RTC from the car.
The Principal of Darkness went from the car to RTC but slowed down.
The Principal of Darkness slowed down as she arrived to the car.
The Principal of Darkness slowly walked to the Willis Tower from RTC.
The Principal of Darkness started at the Willis Tower but ran back to RTC at top speed.
The Principal of Darkness started sprinting towards RTC from the Willis Tower and heard danger, so she sped up.
The Principal of Darkness realized she forgot her cape at the Willis Tower so she sped up going away from RTC to get it.
The Principal of Darkness left from RTC to go to the Willis Tower but she got tired so she slowed down.
The Principal of Darkness ran from the Willis Tower to RTC, slowing down the whole time.
The Principal of Darkness ran towards the tree to save a cat at top speed.
The Principal of Darkness quickly ran from the tree to the car after hearing the alarm go off.
The Principal of Darkness sped up to catch an apple that was falling from a tree.
The Principal of Darkness saw a deliquent try to break into the car so she was speeding up to catch her.
The Principal of Darkness saw another cat in the tree but she was tired so she slowed down as she got to the tree.
The Principal of Darkness walked away from the tree but she was slowing down the whole time.
